productReviews.reviewText: My neighbor Isabela has one of these. She works as a taxidermist and she says it looks monochromatic.
heard about this on folktronica radio, decided to give it a try.
My co-worker Knute has one of these. He says it looks smoky.
one of my hobbies is web-browsing. and when i'm browsing the web this works great.
I saw one of these in Saint Pierre and Miquelon and I bought one.
